data.description: Adorable Country Farmhouse on shy 1.5 acres! Bring the animals and your gardening tools... you have tons of room here for your own mini farm! Gorgeous views of the surrounding foothills. Welcome each day on the large covered front porch with your morning coffee. Enjoy the several mature fruit trees, berry bushes and plenty of room for your RV. Spend the day fishing at the river just minutes away and then come home for a BBQ on one of your two large, covered decks! Inside this craftsman farmhouse you'll find original wood floors, Cozy new pellet stove for those winter nights ahead, stunning vintage hardware, stainless appliances and luxury updates! Cute lil red chicken coop out back is ready for residents!
